GSD.product_version: versions from v3.10 to before v5.10.163
GSD.description:
SUNRPC: Don't leak netobj memory when gss_read_proxy_verf() fails

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.163 by commit 2cd6026e257362f030c8be57abaf7fc0049df60a, it was introduced in version v3.10 by commit 030d794bf49855f5e2a9e8dfbfad34211d1eb08b. For more details please see the references link.
